sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as IntegratedEvaporatorSolver
    participant Trigger as RefinementCriterion
    participant DMesh as dynamicFvMesh
    participant Mapper as FieldMapper
    participant Physics as Phase1SolverCore

    Note over Main,Physics: Start of a Single Time Step
    Main->>Trigger: refineFlag(alpha, gradT)
    Trigger-->>Main: cellsToRefine (labelList)

    alt Cells Need Refinement
        Main->>DMesh: update(cellsToRefine)
        DMesh-->>Main: mapPolyMesh (mpm)
        Note over Main,Mapper: CRITICAL: Map all fields to new mesh topology
        Main->>Mapper: mapFieldsAfterRefinement(mpm)
        Mapper->>Mapper: for (field : allVolFields) { field.map(mpm); }
        Mapper->>Mapper: for (field : allSurfaceFields) { field.map(mpm); }
        Mapper-->>Main: Mapping Complete
        Note over Main,Physics: Physics matrices are now invalid. Must rebuild.
        Main->>Physics: clearMatrices()
    end

    Main->>Physics: solve(U, p, T, alpha, mDot)
    Physics->>Physics: Assemble fvMatrices (A, H, etc.)
    Physics->>Physics: Execute PISO/VOF/Energy Loop
    Physics-->>Main: Updated Fields
    Main->>Main: Write Output, Increment Time